item.title: Advanced Regression techniques on House pricing datasets
item.description: Performed EDA on the Advanced Regression: House pricing dataset on Kaggle. Examined various properties like normality, skewness, kurtosis as well as performed log transformations and analyzed the differences using a normal probability plot.
